title: PPPP M. Farooq Awan wins PS-33 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP) Syed Hassan Ali Shah has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-33, Naushahro Feroze-II by securing 60,617 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Rizwan Ahmed of , Independent, who bagged votes 2791.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 46.32 %.
